### =========================================================
### Product Risk Management Scenario
### =========================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json
@ownerAccessToken = REPLACE_OWNER_TOKEN
@passportId = REPLACE_PASSPORT_ID

### 1) Flag Stolen
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/passports/{{passportId}}/risk/stolen
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerAccessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "policeReportNo": "PR-2026-00123"
}

### 2) Check state after stolen flag
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/passports/{{passportId}}/state
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerAccessToken}}

### 3) Clear risk
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/passports/{{passportId}}/risk
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerAccessToken}}

### 4) Flag Lost
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/passports/{{passportId}}/risk/lost
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerAccessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{}

### 5) Clear risk (after lost)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/passports/{{passportId}}/risk
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerAccessToken}}
